Package: sshub-mcp
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: SSH MCP <https://github.com/OWNER/REPO>
Homepage: https://github.com/OWNER/REPO
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Description: Local MCP server for SSH remote administration
 Model Context Protocol (MCP) HTTP server: projects, SSH hosts,
 and tools to run commands over SSH. Listens on 127.0.0.1:8787 by default.
 Data: ~/.local/share/sshub-mcp/ on Linux. After install:
 systemctl --user enable --now sshub-mcp
